[30;1m17 | [0m[35m    # $2 is the current word or token being tabbed on, either empty string or a[0m

[30;1m19 | [0m[35m    # our candidate list which actually matches.[0m
[30;1m20 | [0m[35m    #[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35m    # COMPREPLY is the list of valid completions handed back to `complete`.[0m
